cat > .github/workflows/scorecard.yml <<"YAML"
name: Scorecard

on:
  schedule:
    - cron: 17

1
  workflow_dispatch:

permissions:
  contents: read
  security-events: write
  actions: read

concurrency:
  group: scorecard-${{ github.workflow }}-${{ github.ref }}
  cancel-in-progress: true

defaults:
  run:
    shell: bash

jobs:
  analysis:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    timeout-minutes: 20
    permissions:
      security-events: write
      actions: read
      contents: read
      id-token: write
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
        with:
          persist-credentials: false
      - name: Prepare Scorecard artifact path
        run: mkdir -p artifacts/security
      - name: Run Scorecard
        id: scorecard
        continue-on-error: true
        uses: ossf/scorecard-action@v2.3.1
        with:
          results_file: artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif
          results_format: sarif
          publish_results: false
      - name: Write deterministic Scorecard failure envelope
        if: steps.scorecard.outcome != success && !hashFiles(artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif)
        env:
          PYTHONHASHSEED: "0"
        run: |
          python -c "import json, pathlib; p=pathlib.Path(artifacts/security/scorecard-failure.sarif); payload={:https://json.schemastore.org/sarif-2.1.0.json,version:2.1.0,runs:[{tool:{driver:{name:ossf/scorecard-action,version:v2.3.1}},results:[{level:error,message:{text:scorecard

check,tool:{name:ossf/scorecard-action,version:v2.3.1}}}]}]}; p.write_text(json.dumps(payload,separators=(,,:)),encoding=utf-8)"
          cp artifacts/security/scorecard-failure.sarif artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif
      - name: Validate Scorecard SARIF JSON
        if: always()
        env:
          PYTHONHASHSEED: "0"
        run: python -c "import json;json.load(open(artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif,rb))"
      - name: Upload Scorecard SARIF to code scanning
        if: always()
        uses: github/codeql-action/upload-sarif@v3
        with:
          sarif_file: artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif
      - name: Upload Scorecard SARIF artifact
        if: always()
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: scorecard-sarif
          if-no-files-found: error
          path: |
            artifacts/security/scorecard-results.sarif
            artifacts/security/scorecard-failure.sarif
      - name: Enforce Scorecard success
        if: always()
        run: test "${{ steps.scorecard.outcome }}" = "success"
YAML
